hopobject.body: Could I have , please? pharma international company russia-cis Absolutely. In addition to the obvious information about the stock market, there are many more subtle financial elements at play in the book. For example, Lindy’s parents are fairly conservative with their money, while her friend Steph seems to always have more to spend. Lindy’s concept of money and its worth changes throughout the book, and I think readers’ will, too. I know mine did when writing the story.
